sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as x402 Client
    participant Server as Resource Server<br/>(:4021)
    participant Facilitator as x402 Facilitator<br/>(:4022)
    participant Casper as Casper Node (RPC)

    Client->>Server: GET /weather
    Server-->>Client: 402 Payment Required<br/>+ PaymentRequirements

    Note over Client: Build ExactCasperPayload<br/>sign EIP-712 TransferAuthorization

    Client->>Server: GET /weather<br/>+ PAYMENT-SIGNATURE

    Server->>Facilitator: POST /verify<br/>{payload, requirements}
    Note over Facilitator: Validate signature, timing,<br/>amount, payTo, asset
    Facilitator-->>Server: { isValid: true, payer }

    Note over Server: Execute business logic

    Server->>Facilitator: POST /settle<br/>{payload, requirements}
    Note over Facilitator: Build TransactionV1<br/>transfer_with_authorization<br/>sign with facilitator key
    Facilitator->>Casper: put_transaction
    Casper-->>Facilitator: deploy hash
    Facilitator->>Casper: poll GetTransactionByTransactionHash
    Casper-->>Facilitator: execution result
    Facilitator-->>Server: { success: true, transaction, payer }

    Server-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>+ PAYMENT-RESPONSE (settlement)
